@DATABASE "Shanghai Warriors"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Shanghai Warriors"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                             Shanghai Warriors
                             =================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(45363,0)"}          45363,0
@{"Lives = x     " rxs "address command zxampoke(37273,99)"}          37273,x (x= 1-99)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
